cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SI, cs.CE 

The paper introduces a novel framework for learning data science models using physics-based models and neural networks. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of neural networks also suggests the category of neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also emphasizes the importance of physical consistency in the results, which suggests the category of scientific computing (cs.SI) and computational engineering (cs.CE).
